      <title>McKesson、Cencora 和 Cardinal Health Circle 佛罗里达癌症专家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/mckesson-cencora-and-cardinal-circle-florida-cancer-specialists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，几家上市药品分销商正在竞争收购私营肿瘤诊所运营商佛罗里达癌症专家与研究中心。]]></description>
