    <item>
      <title>Paladin Energy 计划通过收购加拿大公司打入铀矿大联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/paladin-energy-aims-to-crack-uranium-big-league-with-canadian-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Paladin Energy Ltd. 的高管表示，该公司对 Fission Uranium Corp. 的收购将使其成为第三大上市铀生产商，为投资者在两大巨头主导的行业中提供另一种选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/paladin-energy-aims-to-crack-uranium-big-league-with-canadian-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SEC 起诉 Digital World 前首席执行官涉嫌证券欺诈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/sec-sues-ex-ceo-of-digital-world-alleging-securities-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会起诉了空白支票公司的前首席执行官帕特里克·奥兰多（该公司帮助唐纳德·特朗普的社交媒体公司上市），指控其在公司合并计划上误导投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/sec-sues-ex-ceo-of-digital-world-alleging-securities-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 20:51:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大原油产区发生山火，威胁油砂开采</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/wildfires-erupt-in-canadian-oil-patch-threatening-oil-sands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[炎热干燥的天气导致艾伯塔省各地发生数十起新的山火，大火威胁到加拿大每天超过 40 万桶的石油产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/wildfires-erupt-in-canadian-oil-patch-threatening-oil-sands</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 16:41:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
